{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8af82d75e8","title":"“平反委员会为什么不能由民主党派领导？”","origin":"北京地质勘探学院党委会宣传部编《社会主义教育参考资料第二编：右派言论汇编》，1957年10月5日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"374d407d34","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"8af82d75e8"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7d0fcff003","name":"陶羽忠"},{"id":"82cc012e26","name":"北京地质勘探学院"},{"id":"ba609cc538","name":"党喆"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0621a028d9","type":"title","text":"“平反委员会为什么不能由民主党派领导？”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8af82d75e8"},{"id":"6eebb8ab83","type":"authors","text":"北京地质勘探学院陶羽忠党喆","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8af82d75e8"},{"id":"20dffe893c","type":"paragraph","text":"陶羽忠说：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8af82d75e8"},{"id":"d8029bea9b","type":"paragraph","text":"非党人士可以给他们一个省或一个地方去试一下，看看他的领导情况怎样，平反委员会为什么不能由民主党派来领导呢？这是不是不相信民主党派？","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8af82d75e8"},{"id":"44e79366a0","type":"paragraph","text":"党喆说：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8af82d75e8"},{"id":"0b78bf7018","type":"paragraph","text":"我国法制根本不全，三反时打虎队就是审判员，使得有冤无处伸，人大要赶快制定法律，但是，共产党制定了法律，自己又破坏了法律。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8af82d75e8"}],"page":{"id":"7fa206a1d5","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"8af82d75e8","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}